* Chinese healthy adults over 18 years old ( including 18 years old ) ;
* Weight : male ≥ 50.0kg, female ≥ 45.0kg and body mass index ( BMI ) :

19.0 \~ 26.0kg / m2 ( including boundary value, BMI = weight ( kg ) / height ( m ) 2 ) ;

